{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1696-05_181", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Sur l’Arbre gravé]*"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mai 1696 [tome 5], p. 181-190."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Poëtes, à qui ces choses ont plû, ne les ont pas negligées ; ils en ont fait l’endroit mignon & favori des Elegies & des Eglogues. Les Grecs, les Latins, les Espagnols, les Italiens & les François ont triomphé là-dessus. Virgile que vous aimez tant, est à mon gré celuy qui a le mieux exprimé cet amusement rêveur des Amans. Il est vray, luy dis-je, & je me souviens encore avec plaisir des rives du Mince, & de la Bergere Amarylle. Titire va dans les bois graver ses amours sur les arbres."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Certum est in silvis inter spelæa ferarum"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Malle pati, tenerisque meos incidere amores"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Arboribus."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "C’est un ancien usage, & les Romains, aussi bien que nous, soulageoient par là leurs peines amoureuses. Mais peut-on rien voir de plus tendre & de plus ingenieux que cette réponse ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Crescent illæ, crescetis amores,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Un Poëte de nostre connoissance a dit d’une maniere bien respectueuse en parlant de sa passion à son Rival, qui s’amusoit comme luy à la décrire sur les arbres."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Comme toy dans le sein des écorces profondes"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay gravé mille fois mes flâmes sans secondes ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais ce que mon amour avoit osé tracer,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Le respect aussitost me l’a fait effacer."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Tircis de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[2]", "text": " de Segrais imite plus précisément l’Amant de Virgile, & n’est pas si respectueux que nostre Ami, mais il est plus passionné,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "En mille & mille lieux de ces rives champestres"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay gravé son beau nom sur l’écorce des hestres."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans qu’on s’en apperçoive il croistra chaque jour"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Helas ! sans qu’elle y songe, ainsi croist mon amour."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "On mit ces Vers en air, s’il vous en souvient, & nous les avons tant chantez dans nostre jeunesse. Comme cet endroit touche infiniment, il estoit tout propre pour la Musique, & je ne sçay qui a plus d’agrément, ou de l’air ou des paroles. Madame Deshoulieres a aussi fort heureusement imité cet endroit de Virgile, dans son Eglogue intitulée, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Celimene"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/text()[2]", "text": ", où cette amoureuse Bergere."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Tantost cedant à la force"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "De ses amoureux transports,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle grave sur l’écorce"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Des arbrisseaux de ces bords."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Puisse durer, puisse croistre"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "L’ardeur de mon jeune Amant,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Comme feront sur ce hestre"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Les marques de mon tourment."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Cette Bergere me fait souvenir de l’Hermine du Tasse, qui faisoit la même chose dans sa solitude. Comme elle estoit extrémement affligée, sa plainte est fort touchante."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Sur les écorces les plus dures,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Hermine en diverses figures"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Grave son amoureux tourment ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Quoy que Tancrede la méprise,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Le nom de ce cruel Amant"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Compose avec le sien une tendre Devise."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/ab[1]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/ab[1]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais ce chiffre aussi-tost redouble ses allarmes,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Et luy fait verser tant de larmes,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Qu’elle en arrose tout ce bois :"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Dans la douleur qui la transporte,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Encor qu’il soit sourd à sa voix,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/lg[2]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Elle luy parle de la sorte."}], "a